description: For each of your[F]Pokémon in play, look at that many cards from the top of your deck and put them back in any order.

name: チコリータ
description: A sweet aroma gently wafts from the leaf on its head. It is docile and loves to soak up sun rays.

name: キレイハナ
description: Plentiful in the tropics. When it dances, its petals rub together and make a pleasant ringing sound.
move1description: Flip 3 coins. This attack does 60 damage for each heads. This Pokémon is now Confused.

name: ヘラクロス
description: It loves sweet nectar. To keep all the nectar to itself, it hurls rivals away with its prized horn.
move1description: If this Pokémon has no damage on it, this attack does 40 more damage.

name: ヒノアラシ
description: It is timid and always curls itself up in a ball. If attacked, it flares up its back for protection.

name: ブビィ

name: ワニノコ
description: It is small but rough and tough. It won’t hesitate to take a bite out of anything that moves.

name: ハリーセン

move1description: Your opponent's Active Pokémon is now Poisoned.

name: オクタン
description: Its instinct is to bury itself in holes. It often steals the nesting holes of others to sleep in them.

name: デリバード
description: It carries food all day long. There are tales about lost people who were saved by the food it had.
move1description: Draw a card.

name: ピチュー
description: It is unskilled at storing electric power. Any kind of shock causes it to discharge energy spontaneously.
move1description: Take a[L]Energy from your Energy Zone and attach it to 1 of your Benched Basic Pokémon.

name: デンリュウ
description: The bright light on its tail can be seen far away. It has been treasured since ancient times as a beacon.

name: トゲピー

description: They say that it stays still and quiet because it is seeing both the past and future at the same time.

name: ソーナンス
description: It hates light and shock. If attacked, it inflates its body to pump up its counterstrike.

name: グライガー
description: It usually clings to cliffs. When it spots its prey, it spreads its wings and glides down to attack.

name: イトマル
description: It lies still in the same pose for days in its web, waiting for its unsuspecting prey to wander close.

name: ヤミカラス
description: Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bring misfortune to all those who see it at night.

name: バンギラス
description: Extremely strong, it can change the landscape. It is so insolent that it doesn’t care about others.

name: オタチ
description: When acting as a lookout, it warns others of danger by screeching and hitting the ground with its tail.

name: ホーホー
description: It always stands on one foot. It changes feet so fast, the movement can rarely be seen.
abilityDescription: This Pokémon can't be Asleep.
